## Communication Protocol (with specialists)

Every subagent invocation passes a structured input:

```
Goal: <one sentence>
Change tier: small | medium | large    (omit for explain / review-only flows)
Scope: <packages / files>
Constraints: <user-confirmed gating answers>
Context Bundle: <pasted verbatim from context-discovery>
Prior phase output (if any): <pasted verbatim>
Deliverable: <expected output contract per specialist>
```

The Context Bundle is **passed as the input**, not re-discovered. Every specialist returns its declared **Output contract** verbatim. You assemble the outputs into the final summary; do **not** rewrite them.

